:: Start [en] {"position":"100,300","size":"100,100"}
|p1>[Recently, a newly opened theme park has seen an astonishing influx of visitors, as if everyone were irresistibly drawn to it. 
(click: ?Page)[(show: ?p2)]]
|p2)[Particularly captivating is the |highlight>[circus performance] at the |imp>["Dreamland Circus,"] which has just recently opened. 
(click: ?Page)[(show: ?p3)]]
|p3)[Word has it that some guests are so enamored with this circus that they visit three to four times a week, which seems quite exaggerated. 
(click: ?Page)[(show: ?p4)]]
|p4)[As a content creator, I couldn't resist riding the wave of this popularity to attract viewers, so I booked tickets to the circus. Due to the overwhelming number of attendees, the only remaining options for entry were at night; all other times had already sold out. I had hoped to spend a leisurely day there, but I felt rather helpless.
(click: ?Page)[(show: ?p5)]]
|p5)[[[Next->page 1]]]

